-- Alstom board unanimously backs GE tie-up
-- By Laurence Frost
-- Sat Jun 21, 2014 02:22PM EDT
-- None



PARIS, June 21 (Reuters) - The board of Alstom <ALSO.PA> has unanimously approved General Electric's <GE.N> offer to buy its energy business, the French industrial group said in a statement on Saturday.

